{"tid":1790661,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"幸福賓周又有斬獲","createTime":"2019-12-20T07:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T10:58:46.000Z","uid":253773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ddce500147eac9bb1f7ad9764dae35102c1cefaf","tid":1790661,"uid":253773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:17:00.000Z","msg":"有「女神收割機」之稱的32歲羅天宇（Joey），自2018與前度女友「靚湯」湯洛雯分手後，一直對外宣布單身。雖然羅天宇與湯洛雯金手後一直有不少復合傳閒，可是最後都被湯洛雯落閘，令傳聞告終。<br />\n<br />\n不過近日，有媒體拍到羅天宇與《多功能老婆》演靚女老師Miss呂的戴祖儀（Joey）於淺水灣餐廳食飯撐枱腳，後來兩人放狗兼行沙灘疑似拍拖。<br />\n<br />\n羅天宇與戴祖儀的英文名都叫Joey，似乎頗有緣份。事後有媒體向羅天宇求證是否與戴祖儀拍拖，他回應指當日在沙灘只是朋友間「食個飯」，並透露二人日後或有機會合唱。羅天宇也坦稱與戴祖儀因為喜歡打籃球，由此認識，因為有共同嗜好所以一起外出而已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5idMtA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5idMtA.jpg&h=3223f295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4e63ca3bbbe7fab957af9f1b2a4ec4f44efc66","tid":1790661,"uid":120541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:26:18.000Z","msg":"因為有共同嗜好所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">外射而已，沒有中出</span></strong>"},{"pid":"24c834973db2b4686fa58da4d706ce9d19088f20","tid":1790661,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:27:01.000Z","msg":"幸福賓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686de6c69684e2bd54faed37870a4810c931cfb9","tid":1790661,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"